---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Brisbane Buyers Agent | Save $65k+ | Ex-AFL Founded | 2-3% Fee"
  description="Brisbane's trusted buyers agents. Ex-AFL players Jake & Ely have saved clients $65k+ on average. Access off-market properties, transparent 2-3% fee. Book free consultation today."
>
  <Header />
  <main>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero-section section">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Brisbane Buyers Agent</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">Ex-AFL Players Helping You Secure Off-Market Properties Before They Hit The Market</p>
        <div class="trust-badges">
          <div class="badge">
            <div class="badge-number">$75M+</div>
            <div class="badge-label">Properties Purchased 2024</div>
          </div>
          <div class="badge">
            <div class="badge-number">75+</div>
            <div class="badge-label">Clients</div>
          </div>
          <div class="badge">
            <div class="badge-number">★★★★★</div>
            <div class="badge-label">5-Star Rating</div>
          </div>
          <div class="badge">
            <div class="badge-number">2-3%</div>
            <div class="badge-label">Transparent Fee</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="#consultation-form" class="button-primary button-large">Book Free Consultation</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Breadcrumbs -->
    <section class="page-header">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="breadcrumb-row">
          <div class="breadcrumb">
            <a href="/">Home</a> / <span>Brisbane Buyers Agent</span>
          </div>
          <div class="last-updated">Last Updated: 10 October 2025</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Direct Answer Section (AEO CS-01) -->
    <section class="answer-section section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>What is a Brisbane Buyers Agent?</h2>
        <p class="answer-text">
          A Brisbane buyers agent is a licensed professional who represents property buyers exclusively in the Brisbane region. At Edwards & Smith, our buyers agents have secured over $75M in Brisbane properties for 75+ clients, saving them an average of $65,000 through expert negotiation and access to off-market opportunities in sought-after suburbs like Carina, Camp Hill, Clayfield, Windsor, and Newmarket.
        </p>
        <p class="answer-text">
          Founded by former AFL players Jake Edwards (Carlton) and Ely Smith (Brisbane Lions), we bring the same dedication and strategic thinking from the field to your property search. Our transparent 2-3% fee structure and deep Brisbane market knowledge ensure you secure the right property at the best price, typically within 4 weeks.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Why Choose Us -->
    <section class="why-choose section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Why Choose Edwards & Smith for Brisbane?</h2>
        <div class="benefits-grid">
          <div class="benefit-card">
            <div class="icon">
              <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
                <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
                <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path>
                <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Founded by Ex-AFL Players</h3>
            <p>Jake Edwards (Carlton) and Ely Smith (Brisbane Lions) bring professional discipline and strategic thinking to your property search.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit-card">
            <div class="icon">
              <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
                <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Access to Off-Market Properties</h3>
            <p>We secure properties before they hit the market through our extensive Brisbane agent network and industry relationships.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit-card">
            <div class="icon">
              <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"></line>
                <path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Transparent 2-3% Fee</h3>
            <p>No hidden costs. Our fee only applies when you successfully purchase, and we've saved clients an average of $65,000.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit-card">
            <div class="icon">
              <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"></path>
                <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"></circle>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Deep Brisbane Knowledge</h3>
            <p>From Carina to Clayfield, we know every suburb's market trends, school zones, and investment potential.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Testimonials -->
    <section class="testimonials-section section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>What Brisbane Clients Say</h2>
        <div class="testimonials-grid">
          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
            <p>"Ely helped my wife and I buy our first home. The process was made so easy through the help of Ely and we were able to find exactly what we were looking for, for a price we wouldn't have been able to get by ourselves."</p>
            <p class="author">— Sam Skinner, Brisbane</p>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
            <p>"Ely helped me in every single step of helping me buy my house. He was very reliable and contactable. I would recommend him to anyone and for sure will use his services again."</p>
            <p class="author">— Javaria Mofazzal, Brisbane</p>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
            <p>"Working with Edwards & Smith was the best decision we made. Their Brisbane market knowledge helped us secure our investment property at a great price. Highly recommend!"</p>
            <p class="author">— Tom & Lisa R, Carina Heights</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Recent Purchases -->
    <section class="recent-purchases section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Recent Brisbane Purchases</h2>
        <p class="section-intro">See the properties we've secured for Brisbane clients</p>
        <div class="properties-grid">
          <div class="property-card">
            <img src="/assets/images/outdoor-carina.jpg" alt="Carina Heights Property" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="property-info">
              <h3>Carina Heights, 4152</h3>
              <p class="result">✓ Found after client's 12-month solo search ended</p>
              <p class="result">✓ Perfect family home secured</p>
              <a href="/recent-purchases/brisbane/carina-heights-4152" class="button-secondary">View Details</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="property-card">
            <img src="/assets/images/windsor-4030.png" alt="Windsor Property" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="property-info">
              <h3>Windsor, 4030</h3>
              <p class="result">✓ Off-market opportunity</p>
              <p class="result">✓ Inner-city investment secured</p>
              <a href="/recent-purchases/brisbane/windsor-4030" class="button-secondary">View Details</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="property-card">
            <img src="/assets/images/clayfield-4011.png" alt="Clayfield Property" loading="lazy" />
            <div class="property-info">
              <h3>Clayfield, 4011</h3>
              <p class="result">✓ Blue-chip suburb secured</p>
              <p class="result">✓ Strong capital growth area</p>
              <a href="/recent-purchases/brisbane/clayfield-4011" class="button-secondary">View Details</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cta-center">
          <a href="/brisbane/recent-purchases" class="button-primary">View All Brisbane Purchases</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="faq-section section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="faq-list">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>How much does a buyers agent cost in Brisbane?</h3>
            <p>Our fee is 2-3% of the purchase price in Queensland, including Brisbane. This only applies when you successfully purchase a property. There are no upfront costs, and your first consultation is free. On average, our clients save $65,000 through our negotiation expertise, which typically far exceeds our fee.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>What Brisbane suburbs do you cover?</h3>
            <p>We cover all Brisbane suburbs including Carina, Camp Hill, Clayfield, Windsor, Newmarket, Paddington, Bulimba, Ascot, Hamilton, and more. We have deep knowledge of each suburb's market trends, school zones, and investment potential.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Can you help interstate buyers purchase Brisbane property?</h3>
            <p>Absolutely. Many of our clients are interstate or even international buyers. We handle the entire process for you, including property inspections, negotiations, and liaising with solicitors. We provide detailed video walkthroughs and comprehensive reports so you can purchase with confidence without being physically present.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>How long does it take to find a Brisbane property?</h3>
            <p>On average, our clients secure a property within 4 weeks. However, we never pressure you to settle for the wrong property. Some purchases happen within days when we find the perfect off-market opportunity, while others take longer to ensure we find exactly what you're looking for.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Do you have access to off-market Brisbane properties?</h3>
            <p>Yes. Through our extensive network of Brisbane real estate agents and industry relationships, we regularly access off-market and pre-market properties that never get publicly advertised. This gives our clients first access to properties before the competition even knows they exist.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>What's the difference between a buyers agent and a real estate agent?</h3>
            <p>A real estate agent represents the seller and works to get the highest price. A buyers agent represents you, the buyer, and works to get you the best property at the lowest price. We're on your side of the negotiating table, with your interests as our only priority.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Do you help with both investment properties and owner-occupier homes?</h3>
            <p>Yes, we help with both. Whether you're looking for your dream home on the Gold Coast or an investment property with strong rental yields, we tailor our service to your specific goals and budget.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>What areas of Brisbane have the best investment potential?</h3>
            <p>This depends on your investment strategy. Inner-city suburbs like Carina and Clayfield offer strong capital growth due to proximity to the CBD and established infrastructure. Areas near universities and hospitals often provide better rental yields. We analyze current market data and future infrastructure projects to identify the best opportunities for your specific goals.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>How do I get started?</h3>
            <p>Simply fill out our consultation form below or call us at 0468 479 696. We'll discuss your property goals, budget, and timeline, then create a tailored strategy to find your perfect Brisbane property.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Consultation Form -->
    <section class="form-section section" id="consultation-form">
      <div class="container-wide">
        <div class="two-column-layout">

          <!-- Left Column: Social Proof -->
          <div class="social-proof-column">
            <div class="sticky-content">

              <!-- Stats -->
              <div class="stats-box">
                <h3>Why Choose Edwards & Smith?</h3>
                <div class="stat-item">
                  <div class="stat-number">$75M+</div>
                  <div class="stat-label">Properties Purchased in 2024</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                  <div class="stat-number">$65k</div>
                  <div class="stat-label">Average Client Savings</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                  <div class="stat-number">4 Weeks</div>
                  <div class="stat-label">Average Purchase Time</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                  <div class="stat-number">50+</div>
                  <div class="stat-label">5-Star Reviews</div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Benefits -->
              <div class="benefits-box">
                <h3>What You Get</h3>
                <ul class="benefits-list">
                  <li>Access to off-market Brisbane properties before they're public</li>
                  <li>Expert negotiation saving you thousands</li>
                  <li>No timeframe pressure - we take as long as needed</li>
                  <li>Full-service support from search to settlement</li>
                  <li>Deep local Brisbane market knowledge</li>
                </ul>
              </div>

            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Right Column: Form -->
          <div class="form-column">
            <div class="form-container">
              <h2>Book Your Free Brisbane Consultation</h2>
              <p class="form-intro">Fill out the form below and we'll be in touch within 24 hours.</p>
              <p class="fee-note"><strong>Our Fee:</strong> 2-3% in Queensland. First consultation is free.</p>

              <form class="consultation-form" id="consultation-form" name="consultation">
                <input type="hidden" id="formId" value="ca10e16f-6931-40a3-96c5-d69087bdd5f1" />
                <input type="hidden" id="leadSource" value="Brisbane Buyers Agent Landing Page" />
                <input type="hidden" id="location" name="location" value="brisbane" />

                <!-- Personal Information -->
                <div class="form-row">
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="firstName">First Name <span class="required">*</span></label>
                    <input type="text" id="firstName" name="firstName" required />
                  </div>
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="lastName">Last Name <span class="required">*</span></label>
                    <input type="text" id="lastName" name="lastName" required />
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-row">
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="email">Email <span class="required">*</span></label>
                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required />
                  </div>
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="phone">Phone <span class="required">*</span></label>
                    <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" required />
                  </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Property Requirements -->
                <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="budget">Budget Range <span class="required">*</span></label>
                  <select id="budget" name="budget" required>
                    <option value="">Select your budget</option>
                    <option value="under_1m">Under $1M</option>
                    <option value="1m_1.5m">$1M - $1.5M</option>
                    <option value="1.5m_2m">$1.5M - $2M</option>
                    <option value="2m_3m">$2M - $3M</option>
                    <option value="3m_5m">$3M - $5M</option>
                    <option value="over_5m">Over $5M</option>
                  </select>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="propertyType">Property Type <span class="required">*</span></label>
                  <select id="propertyType" name="propertyType" required>
                    <option value="">Select property type</option>
                    <option value="house">House</option>
                    <option value="apartment">Apartment</option>
                    <option value="townhouse">Townhouse</option>
                    <option value="land">Land</option>
                  </select>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="purpose">Purpose <span class="required">*</span></label>
                  <select id="purpose" name="purpose" required>
                    <option value="">Select purpose</option>
                    <option value="owner_occupier">Owner Occupier (My Home)</option>
                    <option value="investment">Investment Property</option>
                    <option value="both">Both (Live In Then Rent Out)</option>
                    <option value="holiday_home">Holiday Home</option>
                  </select>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="timeline">Timeline <span class="required">*</span></label>
                  <select id="timeline" name="timeline" required>
                    <option value="">Select timeline</option>
                    <option value="immediate">Immediate (0-3 months)</option>
                    <option value="3_6_months">3-6 Months</option>
                    <option value="6_12_months">6-12 Months</option>
                    <option value="exploring">Just Exploring</option>
                  </select>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="financeStatus">Finance Status <span class="required">*</span></label>
                  <select id="financeStatus" name="financeStatus" required>
                    <option value="">Select finance status</option>
                    <option value="pre_approved">Pre-Approved (Ready to Buy Now)</option>
                    <option value="in_progress">Finance Application in Progress</option>
                    <option value="not_started">Haven't Started Finance Process</option>
                    <option value="cash_buyer">Cash Buyer</option>
                  </select>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="situation">Your Situation <span class="required">*</span></label>
                  <select id="situation" name="situation" required>
                    <option value="">Select your situation</option>
                    <option value="first_home_buyer">First Home Buyer</option>
                    <option value="upgrading">Upgrading</option>
                    <option value="downsizing">Downsizing</option>
                    <option value="investor">Property Investor</option>
                    <option value="interstate">Interstate Buyer</option>
                    <option value="relocating">Relocating for Work</option>
                  </select>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="bedrooms">Minimum Bedrooms</label>
                  <select id="bedrooms" name="bedrooms">
                    <option value="">Any</option>
                    <option value="1">1+</option>
                    <option value="2">2+</option>
                    <option value="3">3+</option>
                    <option value="4">4+</option>
                    <option value="5">5+</option>
                  </select>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="referralSource">How did you hear about us?</label>
                  <select id="referralSource" name="referralSource">
                    <option value="">Select an option</option>
                    <option value="google">Google Search</option>
                    <option value="ai-chatgpt">AI / ChatGPT</option>
                    <option value="social-media">Social Media (Instagram/Facebook)</option>
                    <option value="friend-referral">Friend/Family Referral</option>
                    <option value="afl-connection">AFL Connection</option>
                    <option value="previous-client">Previous Client</option>
                    <option value="other">Other</option>
                  </select>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="additionalInfo">Additional Requirements or Questions</label>
                  <textarea id="additionalInfo" name="additionalInfo" rows="3" placeholder="Tell us about any specific Brisbane suburbs, requirements, or questions you have..."></textarea>
                </div>

                <div class="form-actions">
                  <button type="submit" class="button-primary button-large" id="submitButton">Submit Consultation Request</button>
                </div>

                <div id="formMessage" class="form-message hidden"></div>

                <p class="form-disclaimer">By submitting this form, you consent to Edwards & Smith contacting you regarding your Brisbane property requirements. We respect your privacy and will never share your information with third parties.</p>
              </form>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Hero Section */
  .hero-section {
    background-image: url('/assets/images/burleigh-heads-4220-4.webp'), linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(90, 91, 84, 0.85), rgba(137, 139, 122, 0.85));
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    background-blend-mode: overlay;
    color: var(--white);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 80px 20px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .hero-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(90, 91, 84, 0.7), rgba(137, 139, 122, 0.7));
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .hero-section .container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-section h1 {
    color: var(--white);
    font-size: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 20px;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 40px;
  }

  .trust-badges {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 40px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin: 40px 0;
  }

  .badge {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .badge-number {
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }

  .badge-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  /* Page Header */
  .page-header {
    background-color: var(--white);
    padding: 20px 0;
  }

  .breadcrumb-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .breadcrumb {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .breadcrumb a {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .breadcrumb a:hover {
    color: var(--primary-green);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .breadcrumb span {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .last-updated {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  /* Answer Section */
  .answer-section {
    background-color: var(--white);
  }

  .answer-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .answer-text {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: var(--text-heading);
  }

  /* Why Choose Section */
  .why-choose {
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
  }

  .why-choose h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
  }

  .benefits-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 30px;
  }

  .benefit-card {
    background-color: var(--white);
    padding: 30px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .benefit-card .icon {
    color: var(--primary-green);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .benefit-card .icon svg {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
  }

  .benefit-card h3 {
    font-size: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    color: var(--primary-green);
  }

  .benefit-card p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text-heading);
  }

  /* Testimonials */
  .testimonials-section {
    background-color: var(--white);
  }

  .testimonials-section h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
  }

  .testimonials-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 30px;
  }

  .testimonial-card {
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
    padding: 30px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .stars {
    color: #FFB800;
    font-size: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .testimonial-card p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .testimonial-card .author {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--primary-green);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-style: normal;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Recent Purchases */
  .recent-purchases {
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
  }

  .recent-purchases h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .section-intro {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .properties-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 30px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .property-card {
    background-color: var(--white);
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

